      A personal research project by Manav Sehgal. Built on personal time and personal resources. Opinions expressed are the author's own, not those of any employer.
    </p>
    <div class="text-text-muted text-xs font-mono">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8 text-center sm:text-left">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-text-dim">Platform</span>
          <a href="/docs/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Platform</a>
          <a href="/docs/api/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">API</a>
          <a href="/fieldkit/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Fieldkit</a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/manavsehgal/ainative"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="hover:text-primary transition-colors"
          >
            GitHub
